{
  "texts": [
    "The details of the prompts are shown in Appendix A.2.",
    "However, we observed two main issues with the extracted triplets.",
    "First, due to occasional imprecision in following instructions, the LLM may generate triplets that deviate from the standard SPO format, like omitting a subject or object.",
    "Second, the triplets may fail to capture toxic semantics, possibly due to inherent ambiguity in hate speech.",
    "Thus, we propose a self-checking mechanism to refine the extracted triplets, as illustrated with pictorial cases in Figure 2."
  ]
}